om/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fen8opo7ovS4&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm9%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=371fa77d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/en8opo7ovS4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J0mdAnDlG4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ0mdAnDlG4U&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm9%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=b3f6af26\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J0mdAnDlG4U</a><br />\n呢個台灣仔原來咁有料，好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"終於係有人有心機了解三鏡嘅設計理念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf96c20ea5513e256e7431a9742213c9e7d8294","tid":1654020,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n三角排列，三鏡嘅焦點重心會相對近，而且有上下，同左右嘅視覺範圍，zoom in, zoom out 切換<br />\n鏡頭，三鏡同像素，畫質更易一致，相對其他機轉鏡更順暢，無咁容易出面因為焦點嘅<br />\n移位而跳左畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打直（或打橫）三鏡，頭同尾鏡嘅焦點差距更大，<br />\n而且得上下，或左右，一個視覺範圍，zoom in, zoom out 容易跳格，而且三鏡唔同像數，鏡頭出黎嘅畫質不一致明顯。"},{"pid":"b4bb895aa8a00015c54e49f863852e2393c1fe71","tid":1654020,"uid":31962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"到4鏡頭果陣就覺得三鏡原來都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},